PRIVACY POLICIES
Free Slot Games of Las Vegas ("We", "Us", "Our") and its apps including but not limited to Terrible’s Social House and Binion’s/Four Queens Game Quest ("App"), adhere to privacy policies as established by Google, Apple and Facebook.
This informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the App logged in through Facebook. We use your Personal Information only for providing and improving the App. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
While logged in, we are provided with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to your name, username, email address and phone number ("Personal Information"). Like many app publishers, we collect information that your device sends whenever you play ("Log Data"). This Log Data may include information such as the time and duration of your play, status and purchases. This Personal Information is utilized only by us or our data gathering and/or advertising partners and is never sold to a third party.
To request the deletion of your Personal Information and/or Account, click the Contact Support button below, and fill out the form. Allow up to 7 days for your request to be completed.
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this website. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please send us a message by clicking the link below.
